<plot>Yong is a member of a gang led by Eric. Yong had been raised by Eric since he left the orphanage. A martial arts fighter, Yong helps rescue Lily one day. She has an interest in her but his heart goes to his loyalty to Eric. However, when Yong does fall for Lily, he soon learns that Lily is the adopted sister of Eric. Things are complicated when rival gang boss Wong seeks revenge against Eric and Yong. Faced with these complications, Yong must choose: his love for Lily or his loyalty to Eric.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?034732</url></doc>
